'''安·瑪丁·格雷比爾'''（{{lang-en|'''Ann Martin Graybiel'''}}，{{bd|1942年|1月25日}}），美国神经科学家，[[麻省理工學院|麻省理工學院]]大腦與認知科學系教授，同時也是{{le|麥戈文腦科研究所|McGovern Institute for Brain Research}}研究員。格雷比爾主要研究[[基底核|基底核]]以及習慣形成的神經生理學，另相應於[[帕金森氏症|帕金森氏症]]、[[亨丁頓舞蹈症|亨丁頓舞蹈症]]、[[強迫症|強迫症]]、藥物濫用和其他疾病對基底核的影響。

== 研究 ==
在格雷比爾眾多研究中，特別專注於大腦的[[紋狀體|紋狀體]]，紋狀體是[[基底核|基底核]]主要結構之一，與控制動作、知覺、習慣形成、做出決定等生理機能控制有關。1970年代晚期，格雷比爾發現無固定形狀的紋狀體神經元，這些神經元被命名為{{le|纹状质|striosomes}}。<ref>{{Cite journal|url = http://www.pnas.org/content/75/11/5723.short|title = Histochemically distinct compartments in the striatum of human, monkey, and cat demonstrated by acetylthiocholinesterase staining|last = Graybiel|first = AM|date = November 1978|journal = Proc Natl Acad Sci U S A|accessdate = 2014-10-23|doi = 10.1073/pnas.75.11.5723|pmid = 103101|last2 = Ragsdale, Jr.|first2 = CW|issue = 11|pages = 5723–26|publication-date = 1978|volume = 75|archive-date = 2015-09-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924164526/http://www.pnas.org/content/75/11/5723.short|dead-url = no}}</ref>後來研究顯示纹状质異常與神經障礙之間有相關性，如[[亨丁頓舞蹈症|亨丁頓舞蹈症]]與情緒障礙關係<ref>{{Cite journal|url = http://brain.oxfordjournals.org/content/130/1/206.long|title = Striosomes and mood dysfunction in Huntington's disease|last = Tippet|first = LJ|date = Jan 2007|journal = Brain|accessdate = 2014-10-23|doi = 10.1093/brain/awl243|pmid = 17040921|last2 = Waldvogel|first2 = HJ|last3 = Thomas|first3 = SJ|last4 = Hogg|first4 = VM|last5 = van Roon-Mom|first5 = W|last6 = Synek|first6 = BJ|last7 = Graybiel|first7 = AM|last8 = Faull|first8 = RL|volume = 130|issue = 1|pages = 206–21|archive-date = 2014-10-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141024002427/http://brain.oxfordjournals.org/content/130/1/206.long|dead-url = no}}</ref>，以及[[帕金森氏症|帕金森氏症]]與[[多巴胺|多巴胺]]耗竭關係。<ref>{{Cite journal|url = http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v307/n5946/abs/307062a0.html|title = Weaver mutation has differential effects on the dopamine-containing innervation of the limbic and nonlimbic striatum|last = Roffler-Tarlov|first = S|date = 1984-01-05|journal = Nature|accessdate = 2014-10-23|doi = 10.1038/307062a0|pmid = |last2 = Graybiel|first2 = AM|volume = 307|pages = 62–66|archive-date = 2014-11-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141111004627/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v307/n5946/abs/307062a0.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>

格雷比爾後來的研究在於紋狀體是如與認知、學習和習慣形成的相關性。她發現從感覺和運動皮層的神經元投射訊息到身體的四肢，並在紋狀體聚集形成基質（Matrisomes）。<ref>{{Cite journal|url = http://jn.physiology.org/content/66/4/1249|title = Corticostriatal transformations in the primate somatosensory system. Projections from physiologically mapped body-part representations.|last = Flaherty|first = AW|date = 1991|journal = J Neurophysiol|accessdate = 2014-10-23|doi = |pmid = |last2 = Graybiel|first2 = AM|volume = 66|pages = 1249–63|archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304120800/http://jn.physiology.org/content/66/4/1249|dead-url = no}}</ref>格雷比爾的研究接著顯示，身體每個部位都存在著基質，並與大腦負責認知、感知、運動控制的[[新皮質|新皮質]]以及負責協調運動的[[腦幹|腦幹]]連接形成一個迴路。<ref>{{Cite journal|title = The basal ganglia and adaptive motor control|last = Graybiel|first = AM|date = 1994|journal = Science|doi = 10.1126/science.8091209|pmid = |last2 = Toshihiko|first2 = A|last3 = Flaherty|first3 = AW|last4 = Kimura|first4 = M|volume = 265|issue = 5180|pages = 1826–31|jstor=2884650}}</ref>針對囓齒類和靈長類動物研究顯示，基質是形成習慣的重要關鍵。<ref>{{Cite journal|url = http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/cne.903400303/abstract|title = Pattern formation in the developing superior colliculus: Ontogeny of the periodic architecture in the intermediate layers|last = Illing|first = R.-B.|date = 1994|journal = Journal of Comparative Neurology|accessdate = 2014-10-23|doi = 10.1002/cne.903400303|pmid = |last2 = Graybiel|first2 = AM|volume = 340|issue = 3|pages = 311–27|archive-date = 2015-07-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150716081355/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/cne.903400303/abstract|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9753592|title = The Basal Gangila and Chunking of Action Repertoires|last = Graybiel|first = AM|date = 1998|journal = Neurobiology of Learning and Memory|accessdate = 2014-10-23|doi = 10.1006/nlme.1998.3843|pmid = 9753592|volume = 340|issue = 3|pages = 119–36|archive-date = 2014-10-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141023230805/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9753592|dead-url = no}}</ref>

在往後的研究報告中，格雷比爾證明習慣的形成首先激活紋狀體的神經元，接著會激活下邊緣皮質（Infralimbic cortex）神經元區塊。當一個習慣養成後，大腦內會形成該習慣相映的神經元區塊，執行時該區塊的神經元會小幅度激活，並且當執行結束後仍能重新激活。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite journal|url = http://www.cell.com/neuron/abstract/S0896-6273(13)00490-X|title = A dual operator view of habitual behavior reflecting cortical and striatal dynamics|last = Smith|first = KS|date = July 2013|journal = Neuron|accessdate = 2014-10-23|doi = 10.1016/j.neuron.2013.05.038|pmid = |last2 = Graybiel|first2 = AM|volume = 79|issue = 2|pages = 361–74|archive-date = 2013-09-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130929120654/http://www.cell.com/neuron/abstract/S0896-6273(13)00490-X|dead-url = no}}</ref>

格雷比爾近期的研究集中於辨識特定行為的途徑，如習慣養成、學習、認知、決策等，包括帕金森氏症的多巴胺耗竭影響神經元激活及訊息路徑等。<ref>{{Cite journal|url = http://www.jneurosci.org/content/33/11/4782.short|title = Selective effects of dopamine depletion and L-DOPA therapy on learning-related firing dynamics of striatal neurons|last = Hernandez|first = LF|date = 2013|journal = Journal of Neuroscience|accessdate = 2014-10-23|doi = 10.1523/JNEUROSCI.3746-12.2013|pmid = |last2 = Kubota|first2 = Y|last3 = Hu|first3 = D|last4 = Howe|first4 = MW|last5 = Lemaire|first5 = N|last6 = Graybiel|first6 = AM|volume = 33|issue = 11|pages = 4782–95|archive-date = 2019-05-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190520204439/http://www.jneurosci.org/content/33/11/4782.short}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://newsoffice.mit.edu/2013/parkinsons-disease-pathway-0312|title = MIT News|last = Trafton|first = Anne|date = 2013-03-12|work = Breaking down the Parkinson’s pathway|accessdate = 2014-10-23|archive-date = 2014-10-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141029212520/http://newsoffice.mit.edu/2013/parkinsons-disease-pathway-0312|dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 事業 ==
格雷比爾在[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]主攻生物與化學，並於1964年獲得學士學位。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url = http://www.kavlifoundation.org/2012-neuroscience-laureate-biographies|title = Neuroscience Laureate Biographies|accessdate = 2014-10-23|website = The Kavli Foundation|publisher = |last = |first = |archive-date = 2014-10-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141023221006/http://www.kavlifoundation.org/2012-neuroscience-laureate-biographies|dead-url = yes}}</ref>在1966年於[[塔夫茨大學|塔弗茲大學]]生物學科獲得碩士學位後，格雷比爾至麻省理工學院研修，在{{le|汉斯-卢卡斯·托伊伯|Hans-Lukas Teuber}}與{{le|瓦勒·瑙塔|Walle Nauta}}教授的指導下研究心理學和腦科學。<ref name=":1" />1971年，格雷比爾於麻省理工學院獲得博士學位，並在1973年於麻省理工學院任教。<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url = http://mcgovern.mit.edu/principal-investigators/ann-graybiel|title = Ann Graybiel|accessdate = 2014-10-23|website = McGovern Institute for Brain Research at MIT|publisher = |last = |first = |archive-date = 2014-10-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141025192555/http://mcgovern.mit.edu/principal-investigators/ann-graybiel|dead-url = no}}</ref>

1994年，格雷比爾被任命擔任大腦與認知科學系沃爾特·羅森布里斯（Walter A. Rosenblith）教授神經科學職員，並在2001年擔任麻省理工學院麥戈文腦研究所研究員。<ref name=":2" />2008年，格雷比爾升格為學院教授。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2008/institute-prof-1103.html |title = Ann Graybiel named Institute Professor |publisher = MIT News Office |date = 2008-11-03 |accessdate = 2012-06-25 |archive-date = 2012-06-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120603152319/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2008/institute-prof-1103.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 獎項與榮耀 ==
2001年，格雷比爾因其在大腦解剖學及心理學的貢獻，包括結構、化學、有益與運動的思考途徑等，獲得[[美國國家科學獎章|美國國家科學獎章]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.nsf.gov/od/nms/recip_details.cfm?recip_id=147 |title = US NSF – The President's National Medal of Science: Recipient Details |publisher = Nsf.gov. |accessdate = 2012-06-25 |archive-date = 2012-10-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121003065150/http://www.nsf.gov/od/nms/recip_details.cfm?recip_id=147 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

2012年，格雷比爾因闡明[[基底核|基底核]]對於感知及決策的基本神經機制，與[[科妮莉亞·巴格曼|科妮莉亞·巴格曼]]、[[溫弗里德·登克|溫弗里德·登克]]共同獲得[[卡夫利獎|卡夫利獎]]神經科學獎。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.kavliprize.no/ |title = The Kavli Prize |publisher = Kavliprize.no. |accessdate = 2012-06-25 |archive-date = 2012-06-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120621213044/http://www.kavliprize.no/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

格雷比爾同時是[[美國國家科學院|美國國家科學院]]、[[美國文理科學院|美國文理科學院]]、{{le|美國國家醫學院|National Academy of Medicine}}的成員之一。<ref name=":2" />

